Class StaticList<T>

  • java.lang.Object
    • com.github.jonathanxd.iutils.list.StaticList<T>

    Direct Known Subclasses:

    Deprecated.

    @Deprecated
public class StaticList<T>
extends java.lang.Object
implements IndexedListContainer<T>, java.lang.Iterable<T>
    A list with a predefined size. This size is constant and cannot be changed. This List only holds this amount of elements.
